14
00:01:36,009 --> 00:01:38,200
(As graduation draws near,)

15
00:01:39,430 --> 00:01:41,430
(all I can feel is worry.)

16
00:01:43,120 --> 00:01:45,380
(Not just about where to study next,)

17
00:01:45,900 --> 00:01:48,570
(but about everything that comes after.)

18
00:01:50,570 --> 00:01:54,310
